<L>Or felt the con&s;cious tran&s;ports &s;weet exce&s;s</L>
<L>When Gratitude's big tears Compa&s;&s;ion ble&s;s&mdash;<MILESTONE N="1330"></L>
<L>ALMAGRO dies&mdash;the Victor's &s;avage pride</L>
