<L>Condemns the Victims of his power to &s;tray</L>
<L>In drooping Poverty's chill, thorny way,</L>
<L>To feel pale Famine's agony &s;evere,</L>
<L>And all the lingring forms of Death to fear;</L>
<L>Till by De&s;pair impell'd, the &s;uff'ring train<MILESTONE N="1345"></L>
<L>Ru&s;h to the haughty Victor's &s;plendid Fane&mdash;</L>
