<L>Which warm Affection &s;heds o'er Virtue's bier;</L>
<L>Denied tho&s;e drops that &s;tay the fleeting breath,<MILESTONE N="1355"></L>
<L>That &s;ooth the Spirit on the verge of death;</L>
