<L>And ever as her precious tears bedew</L>
<L>Its mode&s;t tints, they &s;hed a paler hue&mdash;</L>
<L>To yon de&s;erted grave, lo! &s;wift &s;he flies,</L>
<L>Where her lov'd victim, mild LAS CASAS lies&mdash;<MILESTONE N="1380"></L>
