<L>Su&s;pends the &s;torm, and bids the tumult cea&s;e&mdash;</L>
<L>Pure Spirit! in Religion's garb he came,<MILESTONE N="1425"></L>
<L>And all his bo&s;om felt her holy flame:</L>
<L>'Twas then her Vot'ries glory, and their care,</L>
