<L>The &s;weet reflexion of its high de&s;ert;<MILESTONE N="1450"></L>
<L><PB N="92" REF="96">
And &s;till her Tablet points to di&s;tant Time,</L>
<L>Stamp'd on its deathle&s;s ba&s;e, his worth &s;ublime.</L>
<L>Ah, meek Peruvia! &s;till thy murmur'd &s;ighs,</L>
